'''Gelsenwasser AG''' is a [[Germany|German]] [[utilities]] company that supplies [[natural gas]] and [[fresh water]] to residents in [[Germany]]. Areas of service include [[Ruhr]], [[Lower Rhine]], [[Westphalia]], [[Lower Saxony]], [[Brandenburg]], [[Mecklenburg-Western Pomerania]], [[Münster]], and [[Saxony-Anhalt]]. The company also provides [[wastewater]] [[filtration]] services.

